{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"34924-bun-thi-kab-nok-khao-khonglav","title":"ສຽງຂັນຂອງນົກເຂົາບຸນທີ","description":"ພໍ່ຂອງບຸນທີຈັບນົກເຂົາໂຕໜຶ່ງມາລ້ຽງໄວ້ໃນຕຸ້ມ. ບຸນທີມັກຟັງ ສຽງນົກເຂົາຂັນ ພໍ່ຂອງລາວຈິ່ງຈັບນົກເຂົາຫຼາຍໂຕຂຶ້ນ ແຕ່ນົກ ເຂົາເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນຜັດໂສກເສົ້າຍ້ອນຖືືກຂັງໄວ້ໃນຕຸ້ມ. ມື້ໜຶ່ງບຸນທີ ເຫັນວ່ານົກບໍ່ຂັນຈັກໂຕເລີຍ. ບຸນທີຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ນົກເຂົາເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ ມີຄວາມສຸກ ແລະ ກັບມາຂັນອີກໄດ້ບໍ?","language":"Lao","langCode":"lo","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sinthanou  Sidavone"],"illustrators":["Nivong  Sengsakoun"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/34924-bun-thi-kab-nok-khao-khonglav"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93888/size3/1ef129b63ff5f374611f1296857cd642.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93888/size6/1ef129b63ff5f374611f1296857cd642.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69156/size6/561517e3aa10dec81afaf160eca088d1.jpg","text":"ເຮືອນຂອງບຸນທີ ຢູ່ແຄມປ່າ “ກຸກ ກູ ! ກຸກ ກູ ! ” ນົກເຂົາຂອງລາວຂັນຍາມເຊົ້າ.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69158/size6/1100fb2456df2481bf1d93f797b5bac3.jpg","text":"ບຸນທີມັກນັ່ງຟັງສຽງນົກເຂົາຂັນ ດ້ວຍຄວາມອອນຊອນ.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69159/size6/8562cd69b6bf1a9dc44f996618c08a81.jpg","text":"ທຸກມື້ພໍ່ຂອງລາວຈະເອົານົກເຂົາໄປປ່າ ເພື່ອຕໍ່ເອົານົກເຂົາໂຕອື່ນໆ.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69160/size6/98a4aa175fd25cc4a6372ebdb4ce5ed6.jpg","text":"ພໍ່ຂອງບຸນທີຕໍ່ນົກໄດ້ເທື່ອລະໂຕ ແລ້ວກໍເອົາກັບເມືອເຮືອນ.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69161/size6/b9dbd9ff0948a01228d29dcac5e8290d.jpg","text":"ເຮືອນຂອງບຸນທີເລີ່ມມີນົກເຂົາຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນແຕ່ບໍ່ມີນົກໂຕໃດຂັນ ແຕ່ລະໂຕມີແຕ່ຈົ່ມທຸກ.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69162/size6/10ac96ac8dc0318d331c7861583e609f.jpg","text":"ເຊົ້າມື້ໜຶ່ງ, ບຸນທີຕື່ນຂຶ້ນມາບໍ່ໄດ້ຍິນສຽງນົກເຂົາຂັນອີກ ມັນເຫງົາ ແລະ ເສົ້າໃຈ.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69163/size6/895e0a480593c7acfe1f2c34be98f343.jpg","text":"ບຸນທີເອົາເຂົ້າໃຫ້ນົກເຂົາກິນ ແຕ່ນົກກໍບໍ່ກິນ.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69164/size6/0eac326e2adc882fd91b875f869d1926.jpg","text":"“ເປັນຫຍັງເດນົກເອີຍ! ເຈົ້າຢາກກັບໄປຢູ່ປ່າລະບໍ?” ບຸນທີຖາມ.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69165/size6/49ce12eb14d103350eaeb235b210a669.jpg","text":"ເມື່ອເຫັນດັ່ງນັ້ນ ບຸນທີຈຶ່ງໄປລົມກັບພໍ່.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69166/size6/84d2ebd11db8828e2dfc0c99ce99dbd8.jpg","text":"ບຸນທີກັບພໍ່ຕັດສິນໃຈເອົານົກເຂົາທັງໝົດໄປປ່ອຍຢູ່ປ່າ.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69167/size6/d35140edf5a638c473385a8deb2a715d.jpg","text":"ນົກບິນໜີໄປແຕ່ຍັງແນມເບິ່ງບຸນທີເໝືອນຄິດຮອດ.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69168/size6/8a623fb629dd85115bb66ab3bb37b4f6.jpg","text":"ມື້ຕໍ່ມາ. ນົກເຂົາກໍມາຂັນ “ກຸກກູ! ກຸກກູ!” ຢູ່ໃກ້ໆ ເຮືອນຂອງບຸນທີ.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69169/size6/50d0633d309e84b90b144eff9bc47b53.jpg","text":"14/14","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":13,"words":39}}